---
const jobs = [
  {
    job: 'Turn loop',
    current: 'Hand-rolled runners inside the Next.js app.',
    pressure: 'Readable, but the route owns too much lifecycle.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Events to UI',
    current: 'SSE from the route.',
    pressure: 'Simple until runs need to outlive the request.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Tools',
    current: 'AI SDK tool definitions with Zod schemas.',
    pressure: 'Good primitive; policy is still separate work.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Policy',
    current: 'None by default.',
    pressure: 'Fine for demos, risky for internal tools.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Budget',
    current: 'Estimated cost only.',
    pressure: 'Useful signal, not an enforcement layer.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Sessions',
    current: 'Browser localStorage.',
    pressure: 'Convenient, not durable server-side memory.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Human approval',
    current: 'In-memory request registry.',
    pressure: 'Easy to prototype, fragile across restarts.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Observability',
    current: 'Logs and UI events.',
    pressure: 'Great for demos; thin for incident debugging.',
  },
  {
    job: 'Deployment',
    current: 'One Next.js app.',
    pressure: 'The strongest feature of the original harness.',
  },
];
---

<section class="not-prose my-8 rounded-3xl border border-umai-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-umai-gray-50 to-umai-accent/5 p-5 shadow-2xl shadow-umai-gray-900/10 dark:border-umai-gray-700 dark:from-umai-gray-900 dark:via-umai-gray-900 dark:to-umai-accent/10 sm:p-6" aria-labelledby="harness-stack-title">
  <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col gap-4 border-b border-umai-gray-200 pb-5 dark:border-umai-gray-700 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="mb-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-umai-accent">the first harness</div>
      <h3 id="harness-stack-title" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-umai-primary dark:text-umai-secondary sm:text-3xl">
        One app, nine jobs
      </h3>
      <div class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-umai-gray-600 dark:text-umai-gray-300">
        The original harness worked because all responsibilities were close to the product. That same
        closeness is also where production pressure starts.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-full border border-umai-accent/20 bg-umai-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-umai-accent dark:border-umai-accent/30 dark:bg-umai-accent/15">
      thin harness
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
    {jobs.map((item, index) => (
      <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-umai-gray-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-umai-accent/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-umai-accent/10 dark:border-umai-gray-700 dark:bg-umai-gray-800/80">
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-umai-accent to-umai-accent-light opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
          <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-umai-gray-200 dark:text-umai-gray-700">
            {String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
          </span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-umai-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-umai-gray-500 dark:bg-umai-gray-900 dark:text-umai-gray-400">
            harness job
          </span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-umai-gray-900 dark:text-white">{item.job}</h4>
        <div class="mt-2 min-h-[3rem] text-sm leading-6 text-umai-gray-600 dark:text-umai-gray-300">
          {item.current}
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-umai-accent/20 bg-umai-accent/10 p-3 text-sm leading-6 text-umai-gray-700 dark:border-umai-accent/30 dark:bg-umai-accent/15 dark:text-umai-gray-200">
          <span class="mb-1 block text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-umai-accent">pressure point</span>
          {item.pressure}
        </div>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
